Interface EmployeeTrainingRecordService

All Known Implementing Classes:
EmployeeTrainingRecordServiceImpl
public interface EmployeeTrainingRecordService
This interface provides a contract for the EmployeeTrainingRecordService. It includes CRUD methods for handling Employee Training Records.
